<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>gCampHayleyBlackstock</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="navbar-header">
          <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbar" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="navbar">
            <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          </button>
          <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">gCamp</a>
        </div>
        <div id="navbar" class="navbar-collapse collapse">

        </div><!--/.navbar-collapse -->
      </div>
    </nav>




    <div class="container">
      <%= yield %>
      <!-- Example row of columns -->
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <p class="lead">
            <img alt="Panel1" class="img-responsive" src="/assets/image2.jpg">
          </p>
          <div class="panel panel-primary">
            <div class="panel-heading">Tasks</div>
            <div class="panel-body home-panel">
              <p>Grouped by projects and lists, just the way you like'em</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <p class="lead">
            <img alt="Panel2" class="img-responsive" src="/assets/image3.jpg">
          </p>
          <div class="panel panel-primary">
            <div class="panel-heading">Documents</div>
            <div class="panel-body home-panel">
              <ul>
                <li>Upload</li>
                <li>Comment</li>
                <li>Revise</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <p class="lead">
            <img alt="Panel3" class="img-responsive" src="/assets/image1.jpg">
          </p>
          <div class="panel panel-primary">
            <div class="panel-heading">Comments</div>
            <div class="panel-body home-panel">
              <ul>
                <li>Comment on tasks and documents</li>
                <li>Get email notifications</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>“gCamp has changed my life!  It's the best tool I've ever used.”</p>
      <p class="text-muted"><em>— Cayla Hayes</em></p>
      <p>“Before gCamp I was a disorderly slob.  Now I'm more organized than I've ever been”</p>
      <p class="text-muted"><em>— Leta Jaskolski</em></p>
      <p>“Don't hesitate - sign up right now! You'll never be the same.”</p>
      <p class="text-muted"><em>— Lavern Upton</em></p>
      <hr>

      <footer>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            |
            <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
            |
            <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>
            |
            <a href="/tasks">Tasks</a>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-6 text-right">
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com">
              <img alt="Linked in" class="img-footer" src="/assets/LinkedIn.png">
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/">
              <img alt="Github" class="img-footer" src="/assets/GitHub.png">
            </a>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/">
              <img alt="Twitter" class="img-footer" src="/assets/Twitter.png">
            </a>
            <a href="https://students.gschool.it/">
              <img alt="Galvanize g" class="img-footer" src="/assets/gSchool.png">
            </a>        </div>
          </div>
      </footer>
    </div> <!-- /container -->


    <!-- Bootstrap core JavaScript
    ================================================== -->
    <!-- Placed at the end of the document so the pages load faster -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../../dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <!-- IE10 viewport hack for Surface/desktop Windows 8 bug -->
    <script src="../../assets/js/ie10-viewport-bug-workaround.js"></script>




</body>
</html>
